fields.name: Self-Assignable Roles
fields.value:
Libertas vel Mors provides self-assignable roles.

Prior to being able to assign yourself roles from this channel, you must first agree to and accept the rules of the community.

To agree to and accept the rules, click the :white_check_mark: emoji at the bottom of the message [here](https://discord.com/channels/1190406648259432448/1195548408182743161/1195548746574991400).
